==English==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Star Trek|(Star) Trek]] + [[-ie]]

===Noun===
'''Trekkie''' (''plural'' '''Trekkies''')

#A fan of the [[TV]] [[science fiction]] series ''[[w:Star_Trek|Star Trek]]''.

====Synonyms====
*[[Trekker]]

====Usage note====
*There is a division between fans over which term &mdash; ''Trekkie'' or ''Trekker'' is appropriate.  Most fans &mdash; and dictionaries, for that matter &mdash; tend to prefer one over the other.  ''Trekkie'' is the better-known term.

